      <title>美国联邦贸易委员会密切关注石油公司高管，寻找与 OPEC 勾结的迹象</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-19/ftc-eyes-oil-executives-for-signs-of-opec-collusion</link>
